  "title": "Project Engineer",
  "description": "<p>You will be responsible to provide an excellent and consistent level of service to your customers. The Project Engineer is responsible to ensure projects are completed on time and are within budget.</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Ideally with an Engineering degree</li>\n  <li>Project Engineer with 3 years of Project Management experience</li>\n  <li>Strong Project Management Knowledge from initiating to closing</li>\n  <li>Able to work in a fast-paced environment, lead the Project Team and manage various stakeholders</li>\n  <li>Result-driven individual who is capable of demonstrating high level of effective Project Management that includes people management, quality control</li>\n  <li>Good set of skills such as cost planning, contract management, creative thinking and problem-solving</li>\n  <li>Candidate with PMP will be an advantage</li>\n  <li>Able to work independently</li>\n  <li>Innovative mindset to support the hotel innovation team.</li>\n</ul>",
